nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 128 is the 106th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 36th published by Titan Magazines. It was released on September 13, 2011.

To celebrate the arrival of Star Wars on Blu-ray, this issue ships with 3 collectable covers and contains a complete guide to the Saga in High Definition! We take an in-depth look at the bonus content, the making of the special features and where to begin your Blu-Ray saga. Plus, Fanboys director Kyle Newman shares with us his love of The Phantom Menace!
